a. Female in dorsal view (scale = 1.6 mm); b. Male in dorsal view (scale = 1.5 mm); c. Genitalia male in dorsal view (scale = 0.3 mm); d. Sterna 7–8 in ventral view (scale = 0.4 mm); e. Female in lateral view (scale = 1.6 mm); f. Male in lateral view (scale = 1.5 mm).
</paragraph>
